        "translations": {
          "en": "He said: Abu Ubaidullah Muhammad ibn Imran al-Marzbani reported to me from Muhammad ibn Ahmad al-Hakimi, who reported from Muhammad ibn Ishaq, who reported from Dawood ibn al-Muhabbar, who reported from Anbasah ibn Abdul Rahman al-Qurashi, who reported from Khalid ibn Yazid al-Yamani, from Anas ibn Malik who said: The Messenger of God, peace be upon him and his family, said:",
